<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>rjʿny tạny llṭryq</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- rạjʿlk tạny wmsẖ qạdr ạqwlk gẖyr ạny kẖạṭy ạrjwk ạrḥmny

[V2]
 ạywẗ ạsthnt bạ̉lạmk wṣlbk wʿmlt ạlsẖrwr ạlly nzʿthạ mny

[V3]
 ạlqrạr - yạlly qwlt ạʿzl sẖr ạʿmạlk mn qdạm ʿyny jạylk yạ yswʿ

[V4]
 ạrjwk nqyny wrjʿny tạny

[V5]
 rjʿny tạny llṭryq ạḥml mn tạny ạlṣlyb

[V6]
 wạṭrḥ kl zygẖạn fy ḥyạty wạʿysẖlk

[V7]
 2- brdt mḥbty wbʿt wsybtk rjʿt ạḥzạny mn tạny tjyny

[V8]
 wạftkrt kẖrwjy wtrky lfrḥk wạsẖtqt lạfrạḥk lmạ sẖft ạnyny

[V9]
 3- mạly ḥạss ạny kẖlạṣ nsytk wnsyt ạnk ạstrạft bḥạlty

[V10]
 dh ạnt lqytny msẖ ạnạ ạlly lqytk bʿd mạ knt sẖạyf llmwt nfsy

[V11]
 4- ạdyny mḥbẗ ạrjʿ wạkẖtạrk wạrjʿ ạqwl mạ ạḥly dyạrk

[V12]
 ạsẖfyny kẖdny ạḥyạ tạny bslạmk kẖlyny ạtrk ạlly ḥbytẗ bdạlk</lyrics>
<author>ʿạdl ḥbyb, ʿạdl ḥbyb</author>
<hymn_number>10338</hymn_number>
</song>